{"tid":109672,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"當你做一樣野開始覺煩厭,你地會點做去堅持?","createTime":"2017-02-06T06:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T02:20:42.000Z","uid":22322,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1c8d40c7cf393fd12b94f8372a51b1d4513b5ba","tid":109672,"uid":22322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:23:29.000Z","msg":"有時做一樣野,成日會覺得唔想做,覺得好辛苦<br />\n好難堅持到落去 開始變到想放棄 你地會用咩方法去堅持?<br />\n舉個例做健身既 相信有做開同有做過gym既人應該都用左唔少時間係gym上.<br />\n仲要每個禮拜keep住操幾日.返到屋企都已經無咩時間..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有朋友方法係搵個競爭對手比自己 覺得人地做到佢無可能做唔到<br />\n依家好多野都想放棄  但又想搵藉口比自己堅持落去<br />\n各位巴打 有無啲咩建議?或者你地會點做?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ea0341558b1c3ce00df197b03ad79f82b6418d","tid":109672,"uid":22322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:31:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba2f561791fe2da8426c5081fc7c5cd20072371","tid":109672,"uid":22322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03a019a6dc85c8346eeaa1128e60255fdb58bba","tid":109672,"uid":22322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:46:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72434d49bec26e82659e5a1ed1b4b12a0b3a863f","tid":109672,"uid":22322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T02:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}